32
00:02:06,880 --> 00:02:07,680
Alright.

33
00:02:48,320 --> 00:02:50,480
Here you are, eat.

34
00:02:50,480 --> 00:02:51,200
Take it.

35
00:02:53,520 --> 00:02:54,480
Eat it.

36
00:02:55,560 --> 00:02:56,760
Chicken represents phoenix,

37
00:02:56,760 --> 00:02:58,080
symbolizing good fortune.

38
00:02:58,200 --> 00:02:59,800
Maltose is sweet.

39
00:03:00,240 --> 00:03:01,400
After eating this,

40
00:03:01,520 --> 00:03:03,440
the master and the queen's life

41
00:03:03,440 --> 00:03:05,960
will be both sweet and auspicious.

42
00:03:07,760 --> 00:03:09,040
The rest is mine.

43
00:03:09,040 --> 00:03:10,240
No one takes it from me.

44
00:03:10,600 --> 00:03:11,440
It's mine, yeah!

45
00:03:14,080 --> 00:03:14,880
I have a feeling

46
00:03:14,880 --> 00:03:16,800
that we will know the truth soon.

47
00:03:16,960 --> 00:03:17,920
Allow me a few days.

48
00:03:17,920 --> 00:03:20,160
I'll improve the remaining dishes
a bit more

49
00:03:20,160 --> 00:03:21,840
