in the Notebook.

53
00:04:44,320 --> 00:04:46,040
How exactly should I cook this dish?

54
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,320
Master, where is your "wife"?

55
00:04:54,200 --> 00:04:56,280
He's occupied with official duties
and he's not here.

56
00:04:56,600 --> 00:04:57,600
How dare he!

57
00:04:57,800 --> 00:04:59,760
Even if he is
the Queen of the Women's Kingdom,

58
00:04:59,760 --> 00:05:02,000
once married, he must honor you
and value righteousness,

59
00:05:02,000 --> 00:05:04,080
abiding by
the Three Obedience and Four Virtues.

60
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,400
And what are those?

61
00:05:06,520 --> 00:05:07,760
Follow the master,

62
00:05:07,760 --> 00:05:08,920
obey the master's orders,

63
00:05:08,920 --> 00:05:10,760
and follow the master blindly
even if she's wrong.

64
00:05:11,640 --> 00:05:14,040
Wait when the master is busy.

65
00:05:14,160 --> 00:05:15,360
Be generous with the master.

66
00:05:15,360 --> 00:05:16,640
Endure when the master is angry.

67
00:05:16,640 --> 00:05:20,280
Remember the master's birthday.

68
00:05:21,400 --> 00:05:22,360
Am I right?

69
00:05:22,360 --> 00:05:23,120
Yes, you are.

70
00:05:29,480 --> 00:05:30,800
Miss A Cha.

71
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:37,360
