81
00:06:45,040 --> 00:06:46,160
I don't listen to music.

82
00:06:50,800 --> 00:06:53,480
Then don't you have a hobby?

83
00:06:59,480 --> 00:07:01,200
Usually, I stay in the military camp,

84
00:07:01,280 --> 00:07:03,560
