watch soldiers lift heavy stones.

85
00:07:03,840 --> 00:07:06,000
I wonder if you're interested.

86
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,880
No, no, not really.

87
00:07:14,520 --> 00:07:16,840
(He's so dull.)

88
00:07:16,840 --> 00:07:19,520
(I know the City Lord forced him
to attend this banquet.)

89
00:07:19,520 --> 00:07:22,120
(But there's no need
to treat me like this.)

90
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:24,080
(This is no fun at all.)

91
00:07:24,440 --> 00:07:27,160
(It's more interesting with Liu Mubai.)

92
00:07:35,520 --> 00:07:37,160
This is Lotus Seed and Lily Soup.

93
00:07:37,280 --> 00:07:39,520
It symbolizes sweet love
and a happy and fulfilling life.

94
00:07:39,600 --> 00:07:41,800
It's a traditional soup
of the Vermilion Bird City.

95
00:07:42,080 --> 00:07:44,320
Also known as Hearts Resonate as One.

96
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:45,560
Also called Lover's Soup.

97
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,800
Lover's Soup?

98
00:07:48,760 --> 00:07:51,320
Princess, I don't know
you can make this dish.

99
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:52,440
Of course I can.

100
00:07:52,440 --> 00:07:53,480
My cooking skills

101
00:07:53,480 --> 00:07:55,000
are just as better as A Cha's.

102
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:58,120
How dare you!

103
00:07:59,200 --> 00:08:00,480
You want to rush in like this?

104
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,440
Yeah, of course.

105
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:03,280
He dared to go on a date behind my back!

106
00:08:03,600 --> 00:08:04,680
I'll teach him a lesson!

107
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:06,520
Dear A Cha,

108
00:08:06,520 --> 00:08:07,680
you fear him not, but I do.

109
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:09,200
He would kill me

110
00:08:09,200 --> 00:08:10,160
like squashing a bug.

111
00:08:10,160 --> 00:08:11,440
The only difference

112
00:08:12,240 --> 00:08:14,280
is that the bug can still have
a complete corpse.

113
00:08:18,320 --> 00:08:19,840
Actually, the Lover's Soup

114
00:08:19,840 --> 00:08:21,920
does not have any special ingredients.

115
00:08:22,280 --> 00:08:23,760
It's made by the women of our city

116
00:08:23,760 --> 00:08:25,320
for their beloved ones.

117
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,000
Therefore, what's put inside

118
00:08:27,000 --> 00:08:29,200
is all the food that the beloved likes.

119
00:08:38,960 --> 00:08:40,160
I really didn't expect

120
00:08:40,280 --> 00:08:42,520
it's not enough for him to bother you.

121
00:08:42,520 --> 00:08:44,160
He even flirted with the princess?

122
00:08:44,200 --> 00:08:45,360
He's such a bad guy.

123
00:08:46,080 --> 00:08:47,240
Why are you cursing him?

124
00:08:47,240 --> 00:08:49,080
That princess said
she came to visit relatives.

125
00:08:49,080 --> 00:08:50,760
