all the time?

126
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,960
She's not here to visit relatives.

127
00:08:53,040 --> 00:08:54,320
It's for a marriage alliance.

128
00:08:55,400 --> 00:08:56,240
Marriage alliance?

129
00:08:56,920 --> 00:08:59,640
Don't you know?
Gongsun Shu told me all about it.

130
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,200
She came here this time,

131
00:09:01,240 --> 00:09:02,440
ostensibly to visit relatives.

132
00:09:02,480 --> 00:09:04,480
But in fact,
she's here for a marriage alliance.

133
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:07,800
